Appium is open source and free to download software which developed using selenium as Base to automate
Mobile Base Applications(client-server architecture) on android ,ios and windows platform.

appium dependencies
node.js
jdk 1.8
testng
selenium webdriver
xcuitest
xcode

appium locators strategies

for ios
id or accessibilityID
xpath
predicate-string
class-string
class-chain
classname
label


for android
id
xpath
classname
label


